<HEADLINE>
<P>
REACTION OF L.A.-AREA JEWS AND ARABS MIXED; PEACE PRIZE: MANY FEEL THAT THE 
NOBEL AWARD WAS GIVEN PREMATURELY, IN LIGHT OF THE CONTINUING VIOLENCE IN THE 
