<P>
 The weekend offers a bundle of made-for-television movies, including today's 
new "Father and Scout," starring Bob Saget and Brian Bonsall, on ABC at 8 p.m. 
(Channel's 7, 3, and 42). 
</P>
<P>
 Also premiering today at 8 p.m. is "Young Indiana Jones and the Hollywood 
