<P>
 The Quiet Zone, a theater group consisting of hearing and hearing-impaired 
performers, will present a variety show featuring music, dance, skits and magic 
at 2 p.m. today at the Curtis Theater in the Brea Civic & Cultural Center. 
</P>
<P>
 The 15-member group has performed at Disneyland, Knott's Berry Farm, Anaheim 
Stadium, the Laguna Playhouse and the Queen Mary. 
</P>
