990-7722. The TDD number is (714) 636-4327. 
</P>
<P>
 The performance is being held in conjunction with a multimedia exhibit, 
"Inspirations: Art by the Physically and Developmentally Challenged," that is 
continuing through Friday at the City of Brea Gallery. 
</P>
