<TEXT>
<P>
 Temple Beth David in Westminster will welcome Cantor Lisa Sharlin during a 
special Shabbat installation service on Friday at 8 p.m. She studied at the 
Hebrew Union College as well as with her father, Cantor William Sharlin. He is 
cantor emeritus at Leo Baeck Temple in West Los Angeles and the head of the 
School of Sacred Music at Hebrew Union College.He will participate in the 
