<TEXT>
<P>
 Quartz Hill 15, Littlerock 15 -- A two-yard run by Quartz Hill quarterback 
Brian Woodward early in the fourth quarter forced the tie at Antelope Valley 
High. 
</P>
<P>
 Littlerock sophomore Devon Reece led all rushers with 165 yards and two 
touchdowns in 21 carries, including a two-yard run in the second quarter that 
put Littlerock (2-2-2, 0-0-1) ahead, 15-8, at halftime. 
