by Woodbridge (5-1, 0-1), which came into the game ranked No. 1 in Division V, 
and sixth in Orange County. 
</P>
<P>
 The Warriors closed the gap to 21-14 on a 25-yard touchdown pass from Casey 
Harris to Marco Hanlon with 1 minute 6 seconds remaining. 
</P>
<P>
