</P>
<P>
 But Nickels intercepted Harris' pass at the Eagle five-yard line with 15 
seconds left to preserve the victory. 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Margarita quarterback Chris Collins, who has been sidelined all season 
because of a knee injury, led the Eagles, rushing for 79 yards in 17 carries. 
</P>
<P>
 But the Eagles had four interceptions, three by Nickels and one by Matt Lucas. 
</P>
<P>
