touchdown with 28 seconds left in the second quarter to give Santa Margarita a 
12-0 lead. Collins connected with Eric Brown on the two-point conversion. 
</P>
<P>
 Ryan Korinke kicked a 39-yard field goal with 6:59 left in the first quarter 
to put the Eagles ahead, 3-0. Korinke's 45-yard field goal with 4:48 left in 
